args.title: Praise: Excellent curation and presentation
args.comment_body:
I just wanted to open an issue to say thank you for the excellent work on this repository. The selection, organization, and overall presentation of the literature here is outstanding and clearly the result of a lot of thought and care.

The curated lists are easy to navigate, the descriptions are helpful, and the structure makes it straightforward to discover new material. This project is genuinely useful for anyone interested in the topic, and it shows a high level of dedication and craftsmanship.

No action required on this issue—please just consider it a note of appreciation and encouragement to keep up the great work!
